reviewText: Like  new.  A great tape , enjoyed it very much  ART
We didn't get this in time for a school project as the first one was damaged but Amazon replaced it immediately.  It is a good biography and video shows Houdini's life in detail.
All I can say is that this video is complete, informable, leaving NOTHING out in Houdini's life and acheivements. VERY GOOD VIDEO!!
For all of you guys who thought Houdini died while performing his Water Torture Cell Illusion...THINK AGAIN!  A&E gives you the real facts about Houdini's life and death! -Diamond Jim Tyler
